ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is the Ethereum Transaction Analytics App?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: It's a powerful tool that allows you to analyze and monitor new transactions on the Ethereum blockchain in real-time. Stay updated on the latest activity, track trends, and gain valuable insights.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app connects directly to Ethereum nodes and ingests data on new transactions as they occur. Advanced algorithms then parse and analyze this data, presenting you with clear visualizations and metrics.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of data can I see?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: You'll get detailed information on transaction volumes, values transferred, gas fees paid, popular smart contracts used, and more. Identify whales, anomalies, and emerging patterns.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: No coding is necessary! Our intuitive interface allows you to simply connect your Ethereum node and start analyzing transaction data right away through interactive dashboards.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app monitors the Ethereum blockchain and analyzes new transactions in real-time. It provides valuable insights into transaction details, sender/receiver addresses, gas costs, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Transaction data is displayed in a clean, intuitive dashboard. Key metrics are highlighted, and you can drill down into individual transactions for a detailed view.

FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, you can set up custom alerts to be notified when transactions matching certain criteria occur, such as high-value transfers or interactions with specific smart contracts.
